org.cripac.isee.vpe.util

Class FFmpegFrameGrabber

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacv.FrameGrabber
      • org.cripac.isee.vpe.util.FFmpegFrameGrabber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class FFmpegFrameGrabber
extends org.bytedeco.javacv.FrameGrabber
    This a temporary version of the FFmpegFrameGrabber found on GitHub. It shall be available in the next version of Javacpp-presets. TODO: If a new version of Javacpp-presets is released (>1.3), use the FFmpegFrameGrabber from Maven dependency.
    Author:
    Samuel Audet
